2017-05-30T16:26:24.000Z","msg":"出面一埋co working space 喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你地平都可以諗諗既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前blueprint 多人就係佢平(2k per head)，而家加左好多人都走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb0b0c5abfc63434f59483d163753d7535db2d8","tid":264234,"uid":33566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:28:00.000Z","msg":"你確定張契俾你咁做?"},{"pid":"ee56ecdd6efca7f0a726b9bf5ba6c0253bae33ae","tid":264234,"uid":3333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:28:07.000Z","msg":"你自己多唔多去下呢D co-working space 睇過先，其實好多係有個主題，去聚集一班人一齊，又或者你本身有一班呢個圈子既朋友肯黎支持你。唔係話整個地方賣下野飲整幾間房俾人就得。<br />\n<br />\n你可以講多少少你自己有乜野資源，如果你話冇架，得一份熱血。咁我只好祝你好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07be0bcc5184d322498df38deb6bad6483ee33c9","tid":264234,"uid":119506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:39:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出面一埋co working space 喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你地平都可以諗諗既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前blueprint 多人就係佢平(2k per head)，而家加左好多人都走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都有留意過，唔同既係我哋每次收費，例如＄100／per hour（一間房比5至6個人用），唔用月費，始終主要想提供高私隱度開會空間，但當然，人哋有本，位置空間都會好啲"},{"pid":"f41eeed0ca1fa0429ba593397358a08d9076c9de","tid":264234,"uid":119506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:39:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你確定張契俾你咁做?</blockquote><br />\n唔多明，願聞其詳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11cad76658967cec2d4bf62b080570fc4b8a13ac","tid":264234,"uid":119506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:43:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你自己多唔多去下呢D co-working space 睇過先，其實好多係有個主題，去聚集一班人一齊，又或者你本身有一班呢個圈子既朋友肯黎支持你。唔係話整個地方賣下野飲整幾間房俾人就得。<br />\n<br />\n你可以講多少少你自己有乜野資源，如果你話冇架，得一份熱血。咁我只好祝你好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有朋友搞緊類似project，之前自己都係Goodxxx member，的確環境好好，聚到一班創業家，但收費方面比較貴，時間都有局限，先想搞24小時<br />\n<br />\n如果講資源，可能只係朋友圈子較大同有人手，有朋友需要呢類服務，始終場地同資金，靠緊計劃書去穩投資者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a7ded5e14e77fc07ca9655a67066ded94579352","tid":264234,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:55:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>出面一埋co working space 喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你地平都可以諗諗既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前blueprint 多人就係佢平(2k per head)，而家加左好多人都走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都有留意過，唔同既係我哋每次收費，例如＄100／per hour（一間房比5至6個人用），唔用月費，始終主要想提供高私隱度開會空間，但當然，人哋有本，位置空間都會好啲</blockquote><br />\n就咁睇好似幾矛盾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n首先有多人房，d 人會expect 可以長放d 野係度，但你個價好似唔係咁吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我一個月用10 日每日8 粒鐘都要成8000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我不如俾多少少自己租一間office<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係唔好講你會24 小時開，我去用都要就住就住個錢<br />\n但你俾人長放野但時租，就變左你自己d 房無左彈性，可能八成時間都無人但又霸住左間房，你又會蝕到扒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果唔俾長放重慘，連呢個賣點都無埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁既收費就咁諗好難做到俾一team 人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知係銅記有一間做緊同你個模式係類似既自修室，都係時租，但佢target 個別人士，1-2人咁反而我覺得仲work 過你個model<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dda48eedc9650fcf5e7e272d398699dedf365f0","tid":264234,"uid":649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:57:12.000Z","msg":"任食任飲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63cf7020db06d020f8d055290b371d9595b88957","tid":264234,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T17:08:23.000Z","msg":"依類唔只提供地方<br />\n仲要配套人才<br />\n租用呢啲地方既我敢講會有一定數量it人<br />\n你要有server畀佢地<br />\n人地startup 唔只要地方，都想人guide佢地<br />\n所以市面上同類型公司會有埋會計法律乜乜七七既顧問去幫佢地，定期搞唔同talk/活動<br />\n<br />\n如果你收時租死得，我做startup你預我一個月幾多日係到做野？我當parttime 間唔中黎一兩個鐘？<br />\nConference room嗰啲可以用時租避免濫用，但要畀錢就唔吸引<br />\n所以靠booking黎限制好過<br />\n<br />\n識人之前做清華搞嗰個tgn <br />\n人地買埋物業黎做都做唔掂要縮水<br />\n你之前諗下可以點做到比市面優勝"},{"pid":"a49c86d9927da6f343f1e1b21c6668a8c5e40819","tid":264234,"uid":101961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T17:11:08.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"b01ecc0f40dc19c371ae57727817955b5f2660ef","tid":264234,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T17:19:51.000Z","msg":"再講多個事實，用得co working space 既都係窮撚<br />\n你有幾無敵既配套都好，價錢一定係最主要考慮既因素<br />\n近期無update 住各區office 月租，但兩年前係觀塘16k 租到一間800 呎左右，鬆鬆地坐得落6-8 人<br />\n如果你target 呢個數目既人最好諗諗點可以令佢地租你唔租office<br />\n如果你target 1~2人就直接同其他co working space 撼，而家佢地應該做緊4k~6k up per head per month"},{"pid":"137f594ab17f707b80ee25d8d222ecf0ce08187d","tid":264234,"uid":14144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T17:23:43.000Z","msg":"創業連張契俾唔俾都話唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點創呀大佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}